**Bitcoin Watch** provides a real-time snapshot of a number of data attributes relating to Bitcoin.

Data Attributes

* Economic size (e.g., total bitcoins generated and value)
* Transaction statistics
* Exchange rates and exchange data.

##History

The site has operated from at least 2010.  On March 27, 2011 the [[Bitcoin_Charts]] service announced it now owned Bitcoin Watch (2.1).

